nodes.text: This rental bay was located in the Elmas private spaceport, outside of Coronet, on the planet Corellia. After the assassination attempt on Wedge Antilles Corran, Mirax, Iella, Wedge, and Myri prepared the Pulsar Skate, and the X-wings of Wedge and Corran in this bay. The windows were blacked out, in an attempt to stay hidden. When CorSec was pursuing Han, Leia, and Lando, both groups decided to leave Corellia together.
